 <span data-ttu-id="4786b-350">В следующем примере C# показано, как задать <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> свойства `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4786b-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
